                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-239-off1277 t18270531-239-cd1278"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 4s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270531-239-victim1328" type="victimName">
